        <p class="text-center img-placeholder"><i class="icon-align-justify icon-muted icon-4x"></i></p>
        <p>About the different types of layers that can be added to a map, including base layers and non-base layers.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-green" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <h3 class="tutorial">Controls</h3>
        <p class="text-center img-placeholder"><i class="icon-cog icon-muted icon-4x"></i></p>
        <p>Controls are the primary interface for map interactions and displaying additional information.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-green" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
