        <p class="text-center img-placeholder"><i class="icon-signin icon-muted icon-4x"></i></p>
        <p>Formats are classes that parse different sources of data into OpenLayers internal objects, such as markers.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-green" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <h3 class="tutorial">Overlays</h3>
        <p class="text-center img-placeholder"><i class="icon-copy icon-muted icon-4x"></i></p>
        <p>OpenLayers allows you to lay many different types of data on top of its various data sources.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-green" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
