        <p>OpenLayers supports EPSG projections for more accurate GIS capablities, well beyond just Spherical Mercator (used in most web map libraries such as Google, Bing, or Leaflet.js.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-green" href="#">View details &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
